  <source>Bispebjerg Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate a possible prophylactic efficacy of photodynamic therapy on the incidence of
      non-melanoma skin cancer, actinic keratoses, warts and keratoses in recently organ
      transplanted recipients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
